Method Detail

getSelectedInvid

public Invid getSelectedInvid()

setAllowNone

public void setAllowNone(boolean allow)
Set the allowNone bit. If allowNone is true, then <none> will remain as a choice in the chooser. If it is false, <none> will only be included in the beginning if nothing is set; it will be removed as soon as anything is chosen.

isAllowNone

public boolean isAllowNone()
Get the allowNone bit. If allowNone is true, then <none> will remain as a choice in the chooser. If it is false, <none> will only be included in the beginning if nothing is set; it will be removed as soon as anything is chosen.
